    {
        "content": "<p>Sure <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/cargo-component/issues/227\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/cargo-component/issues/227</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/cargo-component/issues/227\" style=\"background-image: url(https\\:\\/\\/uploads\\.zulipusercontent\\.net\\/1f57e940f8312ea8a8f75c34d1158652e1dd0a93\\/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f373636616233346231383033356339633438323835356430303133636531666339613239666532353165333532323737613538303638383834316238663764612f62797465636f6465616c6c69616e63652f636172676f2d636f6d706f6e656e742f6973737565732f323237)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/cargo-component/issues/227\" title=\"Error message for not selecting a component should be more actionable 路 Issue #227 路 bytecodealliance/cargo-component\">Error message for not selecting a component should be more actionable 路 Issue #227 路 bytecodealliance/cargo-component</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">I had this .wit file: package example:adder; interface add { add: func(a: u32, b: u32) -&gt; u32; } /// An example world for the component to target. world adder { export add; } world another { export...</div></div></div>",
